                {"swissGerman": "Meitli", "german": "Mädchen", "explanation": "'Meitli' = 'Mädchen'. Swiss word for girls."},
                {"swissGerman": "freu mich für euch", "german": "freue mich für euch", "explanation": "Expressing happiness for someone."},
